uters.com/world/middle-east/turkeys-priority-is-fulfilling-nato-responsibilities-defence-minister-says-2024-08-12/</guid></item><item><title>韩国和美国将针对朝鲜导弹和网络威胁举行年度演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/south-korea-us-stage-annual-drills-over-norths-missile-cyber-threats-2024-08-12/</link><description>官员周一表示，韩国和美国将于下周开始年度夏季军事演习，以提高应对朝鲜武器和网络威胁的能力。</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 06:47:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/south-korea-us-stage-annual-drills-over-norths-missile-cyber-threats-2024-08-12/</guid></item><item><title>尽管俄罗斯袭击加剧，乌克兰仍增加粮食出口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/ukraine-boosts-grain-exports-despite-intensified-russian-attacks-2024-08-12/</link><description>尽管俄罗斯袭击了乌克兰的港口，但今年夏天，乌克兰仍在争先恐后地运送尽可能多的粮食，利用其在黑海地区取得的军事成果来增加出口。</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 05:08:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/ukraine-boosts-grain-exports-despite-intensified-russian-attacks-2024-08-12/</guid></item><item><title>早间买盘：市场转向假期情绪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-08-12/</link><description>韦恩·科尔 (Wayne Cole) 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 04:34:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-08-12/</guid></item><item><title>随着低空经济加速发展，中国试验货运无人机和空中出租车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-test-flies-biggest-cargo-drone-low-altitude-economy-takes-off-2024-08-12/</link><description>周末，工程师们派出了中国迄今为止最大的货运无人机进行试运行，同时一架直升机出租车在即将开通的通往上海的 100 公里（62 英里）航线上飞上了天空，为中国不断扩大的低空运输奠定了新的里程碑——高原经济。</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 03:53:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-test-flies-biggest-cargo-drone-low-altitude-economy-takes-off-2024-08-12/</guid></item><item><title>黄岩岛空难事件后菲律宾敦促中国缓和紧张局势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-file-protest-with-china-over-air-force-incident-over-south-china-sea-2024-08-12/</link><description>菲律宾周一敦促北京重视缓和南海紧张局势的呼吁，此前菲律宾称其空军在两国同意更好地管理海上争端后采取了“非常危险”的行动。</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 03:40:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-file-protest-with-china-over-air-force-incident-over-south-china-sea-2024-08-12/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲足球周</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/week-asian-football-2024-08-12/</link><description>本周亚洲足球的谈话要点：</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 02:21:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/week-asian-football-2024-08-12/</guid></item><item><title>香港法院驳回媒体大亨黎智英推翻定罪的请求</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-court-dismisses-bid-by-media-tycoon-jimmy-lai-overturn-conviction-2024-08-12/</link><description>香港最高法院周一一致驳回了推翻媒体大亨黎智英和其他六名民主运动人士2019年未经授权集会定罪的请求。</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 02:21:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-court-dismisses-bid-by-media-tycoon-jimmy-lai-overturn-conviction-2024-08-12/</guid></item><item><title>香港法院推迟中国佳兆业集团清算听证会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-kaisa-group-liquidation-hearing-adjourned-by-hong-kong-court-2024-08-12/</link><description>香港一家法院周一将寻求佳兆业集团清算的请愿书的听证会推迟至 9 月 9 日，这使得这家陷入困境的中国开发商有更多时间与一些债券持有人就其债务重组计划达成协议。</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 01:49:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-kaisa-group-liquidation-hearing-adjourned-by-hong-kong-court-2024-08-12/</guid></item><item><title>全球股市上涨，而日元在美国数据公布前平静下滑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-12/</link><description>欧洲股市和美国期货周一小幅上涨，而日元下跌，因日本假期消除了近期波动的一个来源，投资者展望美国和中国的经济数据。</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 00:24:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-12/</guid></item><item><title>央行与多头对峙，中国国债市场动荡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-bond-market-rattled-central-bank-squares-off-with-bond-bulls-2024-08-12/</link><description>中国央行一再警告称，随着投资者追逐政府债券、逃离动荡的股票和不断下滑的房地产市场，可能存在破坏稳定的泡沫风险。</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 00:04:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-bond-market-rattled-central-bank-squares-off-with-bond-bulls-2024-08-12/</guid></item><item><title>壳牌与中石油将扩建澳大利亚苏拉特煤层气项目</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/shell-invest-phase-2-surat-gas-project-australia-2024-08-12/</link><description>英国石油和天然气巨头壳牌和中石油周一表示，在呼吁增加投资以增加当地能源供应的背景下，壳牌和中石油已决定扩大昆士兰州苏拉特煤层气项目（SGP）。</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 00:00:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/shell-invest-phase-2-surat-gas-project-australia-2024-08-12/</guid></item></channel></rss>